---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class='w-full h-full px-4'>
  <div class='bg-background_light rounded-2xl py-8 sm:py-16 lg:py-32'>
    <div class='container'>
      <h4 class='text-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-x-2'>
        <span class='inline-block bg-accent size-4 rounded-full'></span>Results
      </h4>
      <span class='inline-block bg-gray w-full h-[1px] mb-12'></span>
      <h2 class='text-black'>We are committed to a sustainable future</h2>
    </div>

    <div class='container flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 mt-14 lg:mt-28'>
      <!-- right -->
      <div class='flex flex-col gap-8 flex-1 text-black'>
        <!-- item -->
        <div class='item bg-accent rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-8 p-8'>
          <div
            class='flex items-center justify-center size-12 bg-white rounded-xl'
          >
            <Icon name='flower' size={36} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class='inline-block text-3xl mb-5'>5,000 Mwh</span>

            <h5 class='text-xl mb-5'>The Crash of Transitional Decision</h5>

            <p class='text-gray'>
              As a matter of fact, the explicit examination of tasks priority
              management traditionally illustrates the utter importance of The
              Skill of Transitional Misconception (Tuan Weeks in The Book of the
              Linguistic)
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- left -->
      <div class='flex flex-col gap-8 flex-1 text-black'>
        <!-- item -->
        <div class='item bg-accent rounded-2xl flex gap-8 p-8'>
          <div
            class='flex items-center justify-center size-12 bg-white rounded-xl'
          >
            <Icon name='flower' size={36} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class='inline-block text-3xl mb-4'>10000 +</span>

            <h5 class='text-xl'>The Accomplishment of Lucid Assessment</h5>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- item -->
        <div class='item bg-accent rounded-2xl flex gap-8 p-8'>
          <div
            class='flex items-center justify-center size-12 bg-white rounded-xl'
          >
            <Icon name='flower' size={36} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class='inline-block text-3xl mb-4'>15%</span>

            <h5 class='text-xl'>The Formula of Inherent Enhancement</h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
